data.description: Welcome to this single-family split-level home in Greenwood Knolls! Your future home offers 5 Bedrooms and 2.5 Bathrooms. The main level has a bright open layout between the Living Room and the Kitchen. The Kitchen features granite-slab countertops with decorative backsplash, stainless-steel appliances and countertops seating. There are 3 bedrooms and 1 full bath  and a half bath on the main floor. The lower level is a walkout, and has 2 bedrooms, 1 full bath, and a stackable washer/dryer. Relax on the big deck out back, with plenty of room for your favorite grill and patio furniture. Located just steps to public transport, less than a mile from Metro Red Line. Call now to schedule a showing!
